== Overview ==
The Ion Flux reactor is another in the lighter [[Ion|Ion reactor]] series. Its advantage over other Ion reactors is its amazing recharge speed.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Ion Flux Reactor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.

